ğŸ” Workflow Architecture
End-to-End Automation Flow:

Google Drive Trigger

Monitors a specific folder/file

Detects new or updated invoices automatically

File Download & Configuration

Retrieves the uploaded invoice file

Reads file metadata

Identifies file type

Routing by File Type

PDF â†’ Text extraction pipeline

Image â†’ OCR-based extraction pipeline

AI-Based Data Extraction

Uses OpenAI GPT models

Extracts structured fields:

Bill Date

Invoice Number

Party Name

GST Number

Total Amount

Data Validation & Processing

Generates system timestamp

Checks for duplicate invoices

Prepares structured row data

Final Storage

Appends verified data into Excel sheet

ğŸ“‚ Extracted Data Fields

The system intelligently extracts the following mandatory fields:
| Field Name     | Description               |
| -------------- | ------------------------- |
| Bill Date      | Invoice date (YYYY-MM-DD) |
| Invoice Number | Unique bill identifier    |
| Party Name     | Vendor or supplier name   |
| GST Number     | Tax registration number   |
| Total Amount   | Final invoice amount      |

